00:01:01,885 --> 00:01:04,304
there'll be no stopping us!

9
00:01:04,387 --> 00:01:06,056
[Giriko roars]

10
00:01:06,139 --> 00:01:07,515
[Giriko] My soul's
wavelength holds

11
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:10,769
eight hundred years
of anger and hatred!

12
00:01:12,645 --> 00:01:14,230
[Maka cries out]

13
