In which case it could
definitely react to the

27
00:03:51,262 --> 00:03:52,764
madness wavelengths.

28
00:03:56,768 --> 00:04:01,106
[Maka] 800 Years of Bloodlust...
Advent of the Heretic Witch?

29
00:04:05,110 --> 00:04:07,445
[chainsaw buzzing]

30
00:04:07,529 --> 00:04:09,489
Are you ready, Maka?

31
00:04:09,572 --> 00:04:10,407
Yes.

32
00:04:10,490 --> 00:04:11,449
Ragnarok.

33
00:04:11,533 --> 00:04:12,951
[Ragnarok]
Yup!

34
00:04:13,743 --> 00:04:16,204
Go Dark Sword...

35
