58
00:05:17,432 --> 00:05:18,808
[Soul]
What?!

59
00:05:18,892 --> 00:05:21,478
Damn it... What now?

60
00:05:21,561 --> 00:05:25,398
Crap...! Great. What do I do?!

61
00:05:26,524 --> 00:05:28,526
What's this...?

62
00:05:29,110 --> 00:05:30,737
It's thread.

63
00:05:36,659 --> 00:05:38,578
Here it is!

64
00:05:38,661 --> 00:05:40,372
There were mass
hallucinations in countries

65
00:05:40,455 --> 00:05:43,249
surrounding the Czech Republic.

66
00:05:43,333 --> 00:05:45,460
Nearly five hundred
thousand people reportedly

67
00:05:45,543 --> 00:05:46,961
saw mysterious, black,

68
00:05:47,045 --> 00:05:50,840
ball-like things both indoors
and outdoors in the area.

69
00:05:50,924 --> 00:05:53,009
No one ever figured
out what they were...

70
00:05:53,093 --> 00:05:54,886
With no other
explanation available,

71
00:05:54,969 --> 00:05:58,932
the case was ultimately
considered a mass hallucination.

72
00:05:59,015 --> 00:06:00,850
People who reported
hallucinations of the

73
00:06:00,934 --> 00:06:04,604
mysterious black objects
described them as spider-like.

74
00:06:06,648 --> 00:06:08,441
[Stein continues]
Spiders...

75
00:06:08,525 --> 00:06:09,818
And the area where most

76
00:06:09,901 --> 00:06:12,862
of the hallucinations
were recorded was...

77
00:06:16,825 --> 00:06:18,785
It was Loof Village!

78
00:06:18,868 --> 00:06:19,953
That settles it...

79
00:06:20,036 --> 00:06:22,914
This wasn't a hallucination.

80
00:06:22,997 --> 00:06:24,040
Eight hundred years ago,

81
00:06:24,124 --> 00:06:25,542
when that heretic disappeared--

82
00:06:25,625 --> 00:06:27,585
she must have split up
her body into the black

83
00:06:27,669 --> 00:06:30,755
objects those people saw.

84
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:32,257
And when that was done...

85
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:35,510
she left her soul
inside the old golem.

86
00:06:42,225 --> 00:06:44,185
What... was that?

87
00:06:44,269 --> 00:06:45,895
Uhhhh...

88
00:06:52,777 --> 00:06:54,904
A spider?

89
00:06:54,988 --> 00:06:56,031
So the spiders scattered

90
00:06:56,114 --> 00:06:58,616
across the world
have finally gathered.

91
00:07:05,165 --> 00:07:07,334
I've waited for this.

92
00:07:08,126 --> 00:07:09,586
Lord Death, it's Stein...

93
00:07:09,669 --> 00:07:11,671
We need to talk.

94
00:07:14,424 --> 00:07:16,217
[Death]
Hey there...! Hiya...!

95
00:07:16,301 --> 00:07:17,635
How ya doin'...?

96
00:07:17,719 --> 00:07:18,595
Thanks for comin'!

97
00:07:18,678 --> 00:07:20,805
Good to see ya!

98
00:07:20,889 --> 00:07:22,474
Well...? What's up...?

99
00:07:22,557 --> 00:07:24,851
Have ya got
something figured out?

100
00:07:24,934 --> 00:07:26,853
[Stein] Yes... I believe
the heretic witch

101
00:07:26,936 --> 00:07:29,397
Arachne scattered her body
and left her soul inside

102
00:07:29,481 --> 00:07:32,776
the golem that's gone
crazy in Loof Village.

103
00:07:32,859 --> 00:07:34,694
[Death]
Arachne?

104
00:07:34,778 --> 00:07:36,029
[Stein]
That's right.

105
00:07:36,112 --> 00:07:37,864
It'd make sense for her
to be the first one we've

106
00:07:37,947 --> 00:07:41,493
seen dramatically affected
by the madness wavelengths.

107
00:07:45,914 --> 00:07:48,249
Even here, I can feel it.

108
00:07:48,333 --> 00:07:50,543
The madness inside me.

109
00:07:50,627 --> 00:07:54,297
Her madness is clawing its
way inside my body.

110
00:07:55,507 --> 00:07:58,385
[Death] I know it's hard,
but try to endure it.

111
00:07:59,386 --> 00:08:01,388
[Stein struggling]

112
00:08:06,893 --> 00:08:08,228
[Stein] This is
too much for Maka

113
00:08:08,311 --> 00:08:10,772
and the others to handle alone.

114
00:08:11,648 --> 00:08:13,983
I'll head there
now to help them.

115
00:08:14,067 --> 00:08:16,361
[Death] Now, now,
Stein, don't be hasty...

116
00:08:16,444 --> 00:08:20,115
I had a bad feeling about
this situation too, you see.

117
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:24,160
Necessary measures
have already been taken.

118
00:08:28,039 --> 00:08:30,750
Look. The spiders are
climbing up it.

119
00:08:30,834 --> 00:08:31,876
They're being drawn into it

120
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:34,462
by the soul I sensed
in the golem.

121
00:08:39,426 --> 00:08:40,844
Crona?

122
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:45,807
[Crona] Don't worry.
I'll protect you, Maka.

123
00:08:49,310 --> 00:08:51,813
[Giriko]
The Kishin has been revived.

124
00:08:51,896 --> 00:08:55,191
Its madness runs
throughout the world.

125
00:08:55,275 --> 00:08:56,609
While you were sleeping,

126
00:08:56,693 --> 00:08:59,738
the Earth suddenly became
a fantastic place to live.

127
00:08:59,821 --> 00:09:01,364
Right...

128
00:09:01,448 --> 00:09:03,074
Arachne?

129
00:09:12,125 --> 00:09:15,128
[Crona trembles with fear]

130
00:09:22,677 --> 00:09:24,679
[Bassing rap music]

131
00:09:37,525 --> 00:09:39,152
[Justin]
I wonder...

132
00:09:41,237 --> 00:09:44,240
Is one coffin going to
be enough for this job?

133
00:09:59,381 --> 00:10:00,715
[Stein]
Arachne...

134
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:03,301
The mother of magic weapons.

135
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:07,972
This must have happened because
of the madness wavelengths.

136
00:10:08,056 --> 00:10:11,393
They've stirred her
at last from her slumber.

137
00:10:11,976 --> 00:10:15,397
[Death] Who knew she was still
alive after all this time?

138
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,273
The mother of magic weapons...

139
00:10:17,357 --> 00:10:18,733
She was responsible for

140
00:10:18,817 --> 00:10:21,695
bringing these creations
into the world.

141
00:10:21,778 --> 00:10:24,406
She used witches' souls to
give them their ability to

142
00:10:24,489 --> 00:10:27,701
transform from
people into weapons.

143
00:10:27,784 --> 00:10:30,787
[Arachne breathing
heavy as she runs]

144
00:10:34,666 --> 00:10:37,210
[Death] She would kill other
witches and sacrifice their

145
00:10:37,293 --> 00:10:40,588
souls in order to make
her terrible weapons.

146
00:10:42,298 --> 00:10:43,550
As a result...

147
00:10:43,633 --> 00:10:46,386
...she found herself being
chased not only by me...

148
00:10:46,469 --> 00:10:49,806
...but by her fellow
witches as well.

149
00:10:49,889 --> 00:10:51,891
[Death]
Where did you go?

150
00:11:20,086 --> 00:11:22,297
[Crona]
This woman... this...

151
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:23,840
...wavelength...

152
00:11:23,923 --> 00:11:25,300
La--

153
00:11:25,383 --> 00:11:27,218
...Lady Medusa?

154
00:11:28,928 --> 00:11:30,638
It's nice to meet
you children...

155
00:11:30,722 --> 00:11:33,016
I've been looking
forward to this.

156
00:11:33,099 --> 00:11:35,435
Maka... Soul.

157
00:11:35,518 --> 00:11:38,021
Last night you had a
little argument, didn't you...?

158
00:11:38,104 --> 00:11:41,191
Over who it was
that burned the curry.

159
00:11:41,274 --> 00:11:43,151
How could you
possibly know that?

160
00:11:43,234 --> 00:11:44,694
It was Soul...

161
00:11:44,778 --> 00:11:47,822
He forgot to turn the burner
off and scorched your dinner.

162
00:11:49,741 --> 00:11:51,993
The two of you aren't
my only entertainment, though.

163
00:11:52,077 --> 00:11:53,286
I've been watching everything

164
00:11:53,370 --> 00:11:55,580
that's gone on
throughout the world...

165
00:11:55,663 --> 00:11:57,374
For eight centuries...

166
00:11:57,457 --> 00:12:00,335
...through the eyes
of my dear spiders.

167
00:12:00,418 --> 00:12:02,712
You too, Crona...

168
00:12:02,796 --> 00:12:06,591
The child of Medusa...
my little sister.

169
00:12:09,552 --> 00:12:10,845
How delightful...

170
00:12:10,929 --> 00:12:14,349
Medusa didn't love you
one little bit, did she...?

171
00:12:14,432 --> 00:12:16,351
Well...
It's not too late.

172
00:12:16,434 --> 00:12:18,228
