173
00:12:24,317 --> 00:12:27,404
[Arachne laughs softly
and slowly builds]

174
00:12:27,487 --> 00:12:29,531
Oh, how delightful!

175
00:12:29,614 --> 00:12:31,616
[Crona seethes]

176
00:12:34,369 --> 00:12:35,495
[Ragnarok]
Go after her, Crona!

177
00:12:35,578 --> 00:12:36,621
Kill the witch!

178
00:12:36,705 --> 00:12:38,331
We're on fire now!

179
00:12:40,583 --> 00:12:41,376
A close call...!

180
00:12:41,459 --> 00:12:42,627
But I guess I have aged

181
00:12:42,711 --> 00:12:45,296
a bit in these last
eight hundred years.

182
00:12:49,259 --> 00:12:50,969
