186
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:11,740
the black blood
with just one kick?

187
00:13:11,823 --> 00:13:13,742
My trusty Saw Leg...

188
00:13:13,825 --> 00:13:14,909
Looks like speed setting

189
00:13:14,993 --> 00:13:17,287
two is enough to
take care of this brat.

190
00:13:17,370 --> 00:13:21,291
I guess Medusa's research
was nothing special after all.

191
00:13:21,374 --> 00:13:22,542
Cuts like that are nothing...!

192
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:23,877
I'll just harden
the black blood.

193
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:26,379
