197
00:13:31,718 --> 00:13:35,388
I guess I'll just hafta cut 'em
in half and eat their souls.

198
00:13:35,472 --> 00:13:36,139
Stop it...!

199
00:13:36,222 --> 00:13:37,223
When you squat it looks

200
00:13:37,307 --> 00:13:39,559
like you're going
to the bathroom.

201
00:13:41,978 --> 00:13:44,064
Now we're talking!

202
00:13:46,107 --> 00:13:47,901
Say goodbye, brat!

203
00:13:47,984 --> 00:13:49,819
Time to die!

204
00:13:51,321 --> 00:13:52,530
Nice try!

205
00:13:52,614 --> 00:13:54,699
Saint Cross Knife!

206
00:14:03,416 --> 00:14:04,959
[Giriko]
Who the hell're you?!

207
00:14:05,043 --> 00:14:07,462
[Soul]
His arm's a guillotine?

208
00:14:08,296 --> 00:14:10,006
So who won?

209
00:14:10,090 --> 00:14:11,841
[Giriko]
Damn, that was close...

210
00:14:11,925 --> 00:14:14,469
That guy almost got me.

211
00:14:14,552 --> 00:14:15,637
It's a good thing I had my

212
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:18,807
chains ready or else
I'd be dead by now.

213
00:14:18,890 --> 00:14:20,266
Quite impressive...

214
00:14:20,350 --> 00:14:22,018
Who are you, anyway?

215
00:14:22,102 --> 00:14:24,104
[music playing in headphones]

216
00:14:27,065 --> 00:14:29,943
Too good to answer me, are you?

217
00:14:30,026 --> 00:14:32,904
[Arachne]
Justin Law.

218
00:14:32,987 --> 00:14:35,615
He's one of the Death Scythes.

219
00:14:35,699 --> 00:14:37,826
This guy is a Death Scythe...?

220
00:14:37,909 --> 00:14:39,202
You're kidding me.

221
00:14:39,285 --> 00:14:41,287
Is he?

222
00:14:41,371 --> 00:14:42,372
