223
00:14:42,455 --> 00:14:44,374
He's a legend at the academy.

224
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:47,377
Four years ago, when he
was only thirteen,

225
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:50,005
he became the youngest boy
ever in academy history

226
00:14:50,088 --> 00:14:52,090
to reach the level
of Death Scythe...

227
00:14:52,173 --> 00:14:53,842
He did it all by himself, too...

228
00:14:53,925 --> 00:14:56,720
...with no meister
partner or anything.

229
00:14:57,595 --> 00:14:59,931
Oh, Lord Death...

230
00:15:00,015 --> 00:15:02,642
Please grant me strength.

231
00:15:02,726 --> 00:15:04,853
