to study right now...?!

259
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,819
Damn, you're a strange girl.

260
00:16:40,407 --> 00:16:42,534
Now I've got
my engine running...

261
00:16:42,617 --> 00:16:44,994
Why don't you take off the
damn earphones already...?

262
00:16:45,078 --> 00:16:46,913
You're not listening to a
single word I'm saying,

263
00:16:46,996 --> 00:16:48,498
