Huh?

265
00:16:51,584 --> 00:16:52,335
I can read your lips.

266
00:16:52,419 --> 00:16:53,753
I don't have to hear you...

267
00:16:53,837 --> 00:16:55,839
Such a filthy mouth...

268
00:16:55,922 --> 00:16:57,757
Quite shocking.

269
00:16:59,050 --> 00:17:01,511
You've been reading my
lips this whole time...?

270
00:17:01,594 --> 00:17:04,723
So you purposefully pretended
that you couldn't hear me...?

271
00:17:04,806 --> 00:17:06,433
Now you're really
pissing me off!

272
00:17:06,516 --> 00:17:07,559
[Arachne]
Giriko.

273
00:17:07,642 --> 00:17:09,352
What d'ya want, lady?!

274
00:17:10,603 --> 00:17:12,897
I detest children who shout.

275
00:17:12,981 --> 00:17:14,858
Shouldn't you know that by now?

276
00:17:14,941 --> 00:17:16,568
How can I help you, ma'am?

277
00:17:16,651 --> 00:17:18,987
The golem's energy is
just about drained...

278
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:21,281
It's time for us
to begin our retreat.

279
00:17:21,364 --> 00:17:22,782
Retreat?

280
00:17:22,866 --> 00:17:24,909
[Arachne] Someone
is waiting for us...

281
00:17:24,993 --> 00:17:26,327
But don't worry...

282
00:17:26,411 --> 00:17:29,456
You'll have plenty of
opportunities to fight later.

283
00:17:32,167 --> 00:17:34,002
There's no choice then...

284
00:17:34,085 --> 00:17:35,879
The rest is up to you, golem...

285
00:17:35,962 --> 00:17:39,549
I couldn't care less
about those brats.

286
00:17:39,632 --> 00:17:42,052
They'll die soon enough.

287
00:17:42,135 --> 00:17:43,261
[Justin]
Hold it!

288
00:17:43,345 --> 00:17:44,846
There's no escaping!

289
00:17:44,929 --> 00:17:46,389
[Golem grunts]

290
00:17:47,432 --> 00:17:48,933
[Maka]
Crona!

291
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:51,478
Maka.

292
00:17:55,315 --> 00:17:56,983
Lord Death's express
instructions were

293
00:17:57,067 --> 00:17:58,485
to secure the academy students

294
00:17:58,568 --> 00:18:00,487
and the trial student
who's with them.

295
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:02,238
Everyone, please duck down...

296
00:18:02,322 --> 00:18:04,908
I'm going to take care of this.

297
00:18:04,991 --> 00:18:06,076
Oh, great lord of ours

298
00:18:06,159 --> 00:18:09,120
who dwells within
the city of death...

299
00:18:09,204 --> 00:18:12,957
May thy name be kept true.

300
00:18:13,041 --> 00:18:16,002
The prayer is increasing the
strength of his soul wavelength.

301
00:18:16,086 --> 00:18:17,629
[Justin]
Oh Lord of Death...

302
00:18:17,712 --> 00:18:20,507
I am your servant of peace...

303
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:23,885
I am a pillar of justice.

304
00:18:23,968 --> 00:18:26,179
I am a blade of faith.

305
00:18:26,262 --> 00:18:28,723
In the name of
the great Lord Death!

306
00:18:28,807 --> 00:18:31,976
Law Abiding Silver Gun!

307
00:18:41,111 --> 00:18:42,195
Now then...

308
00:18:42,278 --> 00:18:45,031
...let us all bow
our heads in prayer.

309
00:18:51,913 --> 00:18:53,498
[Soul thinks]
Amazing...

310
00:18:53,581 --> 00:18:55,583
He's the same kind
of weapon I am...

311
00:18:55,667 --> 00:18:57,961
...and he did all
that by himself...

312
00:18:58,044 --> 00:18:59,671
With my meister
immobilized like this,

313
00:18:59,754 --> 00:19:01,381
I can't even fight...

314
00:19:01,464 --> 00:19:04,342
All I can do is sit
here and hold her.

315
00:19:05,844 --> 00:19:07,262
Damn it.

316
00:19:21,568 --> 00:19:24,195
[Soul] You still can't
move at all, Maka?

317
00:19:24,279 --> 00:19:26,656
Man, that's one stubborn spell
Arachne put on you...

318
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,908
Doesn't look like
it's going anywhere.

319
00:19:28,992 --> 00:19:31,327
I feel so inept.

320
00:19:31,411 --> 00:19:32,829
Uh-huh.

321
00:19:32,912 --> 00:19:34,914
Hey... hold on a sec.

322
00:19:34,998 --> 00:19:38,084
Is it really necessary
to put me in here?

323
00:19:39,711 --> 00:19:40,754
[All]
What?

324
00:19:40,837 --> 00:19:41,755
Come on. I know at

325
00:19:41,838 --> 00:19:43,381
least one of you
can read my lips.

326
00:19:43,465 --> 00:19:45,091
For now I guess
our best bet is to ask

327
00:19:45,175 --> 00:19:47,385
Professor Stein if he
can fix her up somehow.

328
00:19:47,469 --> 00:19:48,595
Yes, I agree...

329
00:19:48,678 --> 00:19:50,847
If anyone knows
what to do, it'll be him...

330
00:19:50,930 --> 00:19:53,516
Stein is a doctor, after all.

331
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:54,851
Yeah, that's true.

332
00:19:54,934 --> 00:19:58,313
I'm sure Stein won't
do anything weird to me.

333
00:19:58,396 --> 00:20:01,399
Hey...
Maka... a flower!

334
00:20:03,610 --> 00:20:06,071
Thank you Crona.

335
00:20:06,154 --> 00:20:08,990
[Maka thinks] I think I
understand how Sid felt now.

336
00:20:18,416 --> 00:20:21,252
A red carpet here in the
middle of the mountains?

337
00:20:21,336 --> 00:20:23,713
I've been awaiting
your arrival...

338
00:20:23,797 --> 00:20:25,674
Lady Arachne.

339
00:20:26,758 --> 00:20:29,844
[Arachne] Mosquito. The air
here has become quite dry

340
00:20:29,928 --> 00:20:32,555
and stagnant in the last
eight hundred years...

341
00:20:32,639 --> 00:20:34,724
It's making me very thirsty.

342
00:20:34,808 --> 00:20:35,934
I have an excellent bottle

343
00:20:36,017 --> 00:20:38,895
of champagne chilled
and waiting for you.

344
00:20:43,525 --> 00:20:46,069
This car's so
cramped and stuffy.

345
00:20:53,410 --> 00:20:55,412
[Giriko]
There. That's better.

346
00:20:59,666 --> 00:21:00,709
Humph...!

347
00:21:00,792 --> 00:21:03,211
You vulgar hoodlum
show some gratitude.

348
00:21:03,294 --> 00:21:05,922
What...? You want a piece
of me, old man?

349
00:21:06,006 --> 00:21:08,425
Never mind your
squabbling, boys...

350
00:21:08,508 --> 00:21:10,051
I'm exhausted...

351
00:21:10,135 --> 00:21:11,970
Hurry to the castle.

352
00:21:17,851 --> 00:21:19,936
[Death] Not only has
the Kishin revived,

353
00:21:20,020 --> 00:21:21,563
but it's madness has also

354
00:21:21,646 --> 00:21:25,275
revived the heretic
witch Arachne.

355
00:21:25,358 --> 00:21:29,404
Yet another dangerous
enemy that must be dealt with.

356
00:21:40,957 --> 00:21:43,793
[Mosquito]
It's been such a long time...

357
00:21:43,877 --> 00:21:45,545
Lady Arachne this is the

358
00:21:45,628 --> 00:21:47,964
network you have
spent 800 years creating.

359
00:21:48,048 --> 00:21:49,466
Congratulations.

360
00:21:53,011 --> 00:21:54,471
[Voices]
Lady Arachne...!

361
00:21:54,554 --> 00:21:57,682
Congratulations on your revival!

362
00:21:59,351 --> 00:22:00,602
Lady Arachne...!

363
00:22:00,685 --> 00:22:04,147
Congratulations on your revival!

364
00:22:12,197 --> 00:22:14,616
[Arachne]
I will defeat you...

365
00:22:14,699 --> 00:22:16,159
...Death.

366
00:22:16,242 --> 00:22:21,247
♪ closing song ♪

367
00:23:46,958 --> 00:23:50,503
[Maka] Justin, what kind of
organization is Arachnophobia?

368
00:23:50,587 --> 00:23:54,758
[Justin humming to music]

369
00:23:54,841 --> 00:23:57,010
Um, Justin...? Hold on...

370
00:23:57,093 --> 00:23:58,887
Can't you read lips?

371
00:24:00,263 --> 00:24:03,975
Hey, Justin!

372
00:24:04,059 --> 00:24:05,352
Whatever.

373
00:24:05,435 --> 00:24:07,270
On the next episode
of Soul Eater...

374
00:24:07,354 --> 00:24:08,563
The Sword God Rises...

375
00:24:08,646 --> 00:24:10,523
Does it Have a
Sweet or Salty Taste?

376
00:24:10,607 --> 00:24:11,399
[Justin]
"Breast?!"...

377
00:24:11,483 --> 00:24:12,901
How dare you speak that way?!

378
00:24:12,984 --> 00:24:15,695
[Maka] I don't think you can
read my lips very well.

